Videos and Podcasts















  

What is Proactive Treasury Management?
Proactive Treasury Management is a new approach to treasury. It gives organizations the power to anticipate, plan and initiate change rather than react to events; optimize and protect cash – the lifeblood of the organization; and deliver strategic execution of their growth plans.



Kyriba ​Risk Management Platform Overview
Learn how Kyriba's centralized solution for cash, financial positions and exposures can give treasurers and CFOs the visibility to make more confident and informed risk management decisions.



Kyriba Connectivity
Kyriba Connectivity provides our clients with the broadest access to banks, integration capabilities, and the most comprehensive set of support and monitoring capabilities than any other vendor in the market today. Through Kyriba’s secure SaaS platform, our clients have access to any of their banks globally, supporting a broad range of formats to send and receive bank statements and payments.



Why Kyriba?
Kyriba takes your treasury function to the next level. Beyond simple productivity improvements, our solution delivers high-level business benefits, enhances processes and provides peace of mind across your organization’s finance and IT departments. Find out more...



Proactive Treasury Management - what could it do for you?
The way we think about treasury is evolving. It used to be just about cash positions and trying to be more productive. However, visibility is key to organizational success - managing risk through financial controls and linking finance teams and the business through technology. Treasurers and CFOs are driving strategy. See how Proactive Treasury Management can turn your organization into a best practice global company. 



